OL,3,CTwo hospitals but just one decision
OL,4,Cover the closure of A&E services
OL,6,FA public meeting is being held where
OL,7,Fpeople are being asked for their views
OL,8,Fon controversial plans to close A&E
OL,9,Fdepartments at either Southport or
OL,10,FOrmskirk Hospital.
OL,12,FThe local NHS says its preferred
OL,13,Foption is to shut the children's A&E
OL,14,Fat Ormskirk and bring all emergency
OL,15,Fservices together in Southport, which
OL,16,Fthey say "will make the service safer".
