OL,3,CTwo hospitals but just one decision
OL,4,Cover the closure of A&E services
OL,6,FA joint committee of NHS trusts
OL,7,FShaping Care Together says change is
OL,8,Fneeded because they are facing five
OL,9,Fmajor pressures on services: people
OL,10,Fare living longer and need more care,
OL,11,Fgetting and keeping staff, maintaining
OL,12,Fhigh standards of care, having
OL,13,Fbuildings that meet patients needs and
OL,14,Fhaving enough money.
OL,16,FThe committee behind the plans says
OL,17,F"no decisions have been made" and
OL,18,Fresidents are being urged to share
OL,19,Ftheir experience in consultation that
OL,20,Fruns until 3rd October.
