OL,3,CTwo hospitals but just one decision
OL,4,Cover the closure of A&E services
OL,6,FDr Kate Clark from Mersey and West
OL,7,FLancashire Hospitals NHS Trust said:
OL,8,F"We are not closing, we are trying to
OL,9,Fgive better provision. It might not be
OL,10,Fin the same place but at the moment we
OL,11,Fhave children who have to go
OL,12,Fsignificantly further away if they
OL,13,Fbecome unwell overnight and need an A
OL,14,F& E. We want to be able to provide
OL,15,Fthat 24 hours a day."
OL,17,FA series of public meetings are taking
OL,18,Fplace, including in Aughton near
OL,19,FOrmskirk on Tuesday 23rd September and
OL,20,FSouthport on Tuesday 30th September.
